ekty</a></li><li><a href="/finansowanie-nauki/dla-ekspertow">Dla ekspertów</a></li><li><a href="/finansowanie-nauki/koszty-w-projektach">Koszty w projektach badawczych</a></li><li><a href="/finansowanie-nauki/faq">Najczęściej zadawane pytania</a></li><li><a href="/statystyki">Statystyki konkursów</a></li><li class="wazne"><a href="/baza-ofert/">Oferty pracy w projektach</a></li></ul></div></div><div id="block-views-calendar2-block-1" class="block block-views"><h2>Kalendarz wydarzeń</h2><div class="content"><div class="view view-calendar2 view-id-calendar2 view-display-id-block_1 view-dom-id-502cc2c92d99a98389f5a52ba57c1fdf"><div class="view-header"><div class="date-nav-wrapper clearfix"><div class="date-nav item-list"><div class="date-heading"><h3><a href="http://ncn.gov.pl/kalendarz/miesiac/2018-03" title="View full page month">Marzec</a></h3></div><ul class="pager"><li class="date-prev"> <a href="http://ncn.gov.pl/aktualnosci-glowna?mini=2018-02" title="Navigate to previous month" rel="nofollow">&laquo;</a></li><li class="date-next"> <a href="http://ncn.gov.pl/aktualnosci-glowna?mini=2018-04" title="Navigate to next month" rel="nofollow">&raquo;</a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="view-content"><div class="calendar-calendar"><div class="month-view"><table class="mini"><thead><tr><th class="days mon"> p</th><th class="days tue"> w</th><th class="days wed"> ś</th><th class="days thu"> c</th><th class="days fri"> p</th><th class="days sat"> s</th><th class="days sun"> n</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td id="calendar2-2018-02-26" class="mon mini empty"><div class="calendar-empty">&nbsp;</div></td><td id="calendar2-2018-02-27" class="tue mini empty"><div class="calendar-empty">&nbsp;</div></td><td id="calendar2-2018-02-28" class="wed mini empty"><div class="calendar-empty">&nbsp;</div></td><td id="calendar2-2018-03-01" class="thu mini past has-events"><div class="month mini-day-on"> <a href="http://ncn.gov.pl/kalendarz/dzien/2018-03-01">1</a><div class="calendar_t